Vice President Biden will deliver remarks on the progress of the American Recovery and Reinvestment Act and the overall state of the economy at the Brookings Institution. The event is scheduled for September 3 at 10:00 AM EDT and is open to the press. Media details, including camera preset times and press arrival times, are provided in the article. Media outlets must RSVP by September 2 at 3:00 PM EDT and wear their media credentials at all times during the event. Press logistics questions can be directed to Nora Cohen at 202-503-5568.